like a year ago i bought a webcam and installed it with the installation cd. now when i bought a new computer i needed the cd to install the cam again but couldn't find it. and i didn't want to buy a new webcam just because i lost my cd. so i search the internet and finally i found the driver that was needed for the webcam. so here it is for all you guys that might need it.
you can stop searching, you have found it!

Enjoy!
